                  </hi>. These are my earrings.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> She put the earrings into my ears, and I went to a coffee-shop for my breakfast; I did not steal them—I stayed there till Monday morning.</p>
